ABOUT
=====
The pajas module is a collection of tools and extensions to Kohana.

It is compatible with version 3.1.x


INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
=========================
* Create a folder named "pajas" in your modules directory in your kohana v3.2 install
* Copy all pajas files to that folder
* Add pajas to your activated modules in application/bootstrap.php
* Setup your database in pajas/config/pdo.php
* Create application/user_content and make it writeable

or use git:

* cd path-to-kohana/modules
* git clone git://github.com/lillem4n/kohana-module-pajas.git pajas
* Setup your database in pajas/config/pdo.php
* Create application/user_content and make it writeable

To see the example controller on a clean install, rename or remove
application/classes/controller/welcome.php.


DOCUMENATION
============
